6
00:00:24,832 --> 00:00:25,962
He suddenly fell.

7
00:00:25,962 --> 00:00:27,403
Hurry!

8
00:00:31,101 --> 00:00:32,371
Mr. Shin,

9
00:00:32,631 --> 00:00:34,142
they gave me this at the reception.

10
